Significant changes made in this fork (from 2026-06-14 onward):

  - Replaced Termy's unauthenticated localhost WebSocket transport with
    OS-authenticated transports: a Windows named pipe (per-user DACL), a Unix
    domain socket (mode 0600 inside a per-user 0700 directory) on macOS and
    Linux, and a 256-bit capability-token authenticated WebSocket as a
    fallback.

  - Added a daemon-owned session model so terminal sessions survive an
    Obsidian reload: bounded output replay, reattach by session id, orphan
    timeouts, and re-discovery after a full reload.

  - Changed server-binary distribution to fetch only from this project's own
    GitHub release host (removing the third-party binary host), with build
    provenance attestation.

